languages.text: "Из Комморры нет безопасного пути. Ты лжешь сама себе и этим несчастным. Куда бы ты их ни направила — в Темном городе мон-кай ждут лишь смерть и страдания".
"There is no safe way out of Commorragh. You are lying to yourself and to these poor people. Wherever you send them, the Dark City holds only death and misery for mon-keigh."

languages.text: 「コモラフから安全に脱出する方法なんてない。あなたは自分自身に、そしてこの哀れな者たちに嘘をついている。彼らをどこに送ろうとも、仄暗き都にいるモン＝ケイには死と苦痛しかない」
languages.original_text: "There is no safe way out of Commorragh. You are lying to yourself and to these poor people. Wherever you send them, the Dark City holds only death and misery for mon-keigh."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: “根本没有安全的道路可以离开科摩罗。你不过是在自欺欺人，欺骗这些可怜人罢了。无论你把他们送到哪里，黑暗之城只会给猴子带来痛苦与死亡。”
languages.original_text: "There is no safe way out of Commorragh. You are lying to yourself and to these poor people. Wherever you send them, the Dark City holds only death and misery for mon-keigh."

languages.text: «No hay ninguna forma segura de salir de Commorragh. Se está mintiendo a sí misma y a esta pobre gente. Los mande donde los mande, la Ciudad Siniestra solo tiene muerte y miseria para los mon-keigh».
languages.original_text: "There is no safe way out of Commorragh. You are lying to yourself and to these poor people. Wherever you send them, the Dark City holds only death and misery for mon-keigh."

languages.text: "Es gibt keinen sicheren Weg aus Commorragh heraus. Ihr macht Euch selbst und diesen armen Leuten etwas vor. Wohin Ihr sie auch schickt, die Dunkle Stadt hält für die Chem-Pan-Sey nur Tod und Elend bereit."

languages.text: « Il n'y a aucun moyen de quitter Commorragh en toute sécurité, comme vous dites. Vous vous mentez à vous-même et à ces pauvres malheureux. La mort et la souffrance, voilà tout ce qui attend les mon-keigh dans la Cité Crépusculaire. »
languages.original_text: "There is no safe way out of Commorragh. You are lying to yourself and to these poor people. Wherever you send them, the Dark City holds only death and misery for mon-keigh."

languages.text: "Commorragh'tan çıkmanın güvenli bir yolu yoktur. Hem kendini hem de o zavallıları kandırıyorsun. Onları her nereye gönderirsen gönder, Kara Şehir'de mon-keighler için ölüm ve ızdıraptan başka hiçbir şey bulamazsın."
